#

Paneer Shawarma with Fries and Spicy Mayo

$15.99
800 kcal

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianIndian

Tags:

Indian CuisineStreet FoodVegetarian Delight

Description

A tantalizing twist on traditional shawarma featuring spiced paneer, crispy fries, and a punch of spicy mayo, all wrapped in a soft flatbread with fresh veggies.

Ingredients

  • Paneer: 400g
  • Pita bread: 4 pieces
  • Cucumber: 1, sliced
  • Tomato: 2, sliced
  • Lettuce: 1 cup, shredded
  • Potato: 2 large, for fries
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • Paprika: 1 tsp
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Chili powder: 1 tsp
  • Mayonnaise: 1/2 cup
  • Sriracha sauce: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
